    {
      "text": "Chasing novelty over value:",
      "x": 49.6,
      "y": 189.4,
      "w": 207.4,
      "h": 17.9,
      "font": "HendersonBCGSans-Bold",
      "size": 16.0,
      "color": "#e71c57",
      "flags": 16
    },
    {
      "text": " Teams pursue new AI or agent technologies without anchoring on high-impact telco use ",
      "x": 257.1,
      "y": 189.4,
      "w": 625.3,
      "h": 17.9,
      "font": "HendersonBCGSans-Regular",
      "size": 16.0,
      "color": "#000000",
      "flags": 0
    },
    {
      "text": "cases — diluting capital, and leadership attention",
      "x": 49.6,
      "y": 208.7,
      "w": 349.3,
      "h": 17.9,
      "font": "HendersonBCGSans-Regular",
      "size": 16.0,
      "color": "#000000",
      "flags": 0
    },
    {
      "text": "Skipping early data readiness:",
      "x": 49.6,
      "y": 254.0,
      "w": 229.0,
      "h": 17.9,
      "font": "HendersonBCGSans-Bold",
      "size": 16.0,
      "color": "#e71c57",
      "flags": 16
    },
    {
      "text": " Agents are built on siloed or low-quality OSS/BSS, network, or customer data, with ",
      "x": 278.8,
      "y": 254.0,
      "w": 583.2,
      "h": 17.9,
      "font": "HendersonBCGSans-Regular",
      "size": 16.0,
      "color": "#000000",
      "flags": 0
    },
    {
      "text": "fragmented ownership across functions",
      "x": 49.6,
      "y": 273.2,
      "w": 277.1,
      "h": 17.9,
      "font": "HendersonBCGSans-Regular",
      "size": 16.0,
      "color": "#000000",
      "flags": 0
    },
    {
      "text": "Running pilots in isolation:",
      "x": 49.6,
      "y": 318.6,
      "w": 204.8,
      "h": 17.9,
      "font": "HendersonBCGSans-Bold",
      "size": 16.0,
      "color": "#e71c57",
      "flags": 16
    },
    {
      "text": " Solutions stay stuck as proofs of concept, disconnected from core workflows, systems, ",
      "x": 254.6,
      "y": 318.6,
      "w": 605.6,
      "h": 17.9,
      "font": "HendersonBCGSans-Regular",
      "size": 16.0,
      "color": "#000000",
      "flags": 0
    },
    {
      "text": "and automation; insights don’t move to action",
      "x": 49.6,
      "y": 337.8,
      "w": 324.6,
      "h": 17.9,
      "font": "HendersonBCGSans-Regular",
      "size": 16.0,
      "color": "#000000",
      "flags": 0
    },
    {
      "text": "Underestimating scale and compliance:",
      "x": 49.6,
      "y": 383.2,
      "w": 301.4,
      "h": 17.9,
      "font": "HendersonBCGSans-Bold",
      "size": 16.0,
      "color": "#e71c57",
      "flags": 16
    },
    {
      "text": " One-off pilots don’t build reusable platforms; regulatory, security, and change ",
      "x": 351.3,
      "y": 383.2,
      "w": 551.1,
      "h": 17.9,
      "font": "HendersonBCGSans-Regular",
      "size": 16.0,
      "color": "#000000",
      "flags": 0
    },
    {
      "text": "management gaps stall enterprise rollout",
      "x": 49.6,
      "y": 402.4,
      "w": 291.3,
      "h": 17.9,
      "font": "HendersonBCGSans-Regular",
      "size": 16.0,
      "color": "#000000",
      "flags": 0
    },
    {
      "text": "Treating AI as IT spending:",
      "x": 49.6,
      "y": 447.7,
      "w": 204.1,
      "h": 17.9,
      "font": "HendersonBCGSans-Bold",
      "size": 16.0,
      "color": "#e71c57",
      "flags": 16
    },
    {
      "text": " AI and agents are funded as technology initiatives rather than business capabilities tied to ",
      "x": 253.8,
      "y": 447.7,
      "w": 643.9,
      "h": 17.9,
      "font": "HendersonBCGSans-Regular",
      "size": 16.0,
      "color": "#000000",
      "flags": 0
    },
    {
      "text": "KPIs, leading to low ROI and stalled scaling",
      "x": 49.6,
      "y": 466.9,
      "w": 304.1,
      "h": 17.9,
      "font": "HendersonBCGSans-Regular",
      "size": 16.0,
      "color": "#000000",
      "flags": 0
    },
    {
      "text": "Risks | ",
      "x": 49.6,
      "y": 31.9,
      "w": 80.4,
      "h": 26.9,
      "font": "HendersonBCGSans-Bold",
      "size": 24.0,
      "color": "#41ff94",
      "flags": 16
    },
    {
      "text": "Avoid these common pitfalls in AI transformation",
